{
  "stateName": "Uttar Pradesh",
  "documentType": "ration_card",
  "commonIssues": "<!-- 1. Name not in List -->\n<div class=\"card mb-2\">\n    <div class=\"card-header\" id=\"headingUP1\">\n        <h5 class=\"mb-0\">\n            <button class=\"btn btn-link text-left\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#collapseUP1\" style=\"white-space: normal; word-break: break-word;\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-right mr-2\"></i>Name Missing from \"Patrata Suchi\" (Eligibility List)\n            </button>\n        </h5>\n    </div>\n    <div id=\"collapseUP1\" class=\"collapse\">\n        <div class=\"card-body\">\n            <p>Sometimes cards are cancelled during periodic audits if e-KYC is not done or if the family is found ineligible.</p>\n            <p><strong>How to fix:</strong></p>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Check your status on the <a href=\"https://fcs.up.gov.in/\" target=\"_blank\">UP FCS portal</a> using your Ration Card ID.</li>\n                <li>If cancelled, visit the <strong>Tehsil Supply Office</strong> with Aadhaar and income proof for restoration.</li>\n                <li>Ensure <strong>biometric e-KYC</strong> is done at the FPS shop immediately.</li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- 2. Unit Error -->\n<div class=\"card mb-2\">\n    <div class=\"card-header\" id=\"headingUP2\">\n        <h5 class=\"mb-0\">\n            <button class=\"btn btn-link text-left collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#collapseUP2\" style=\"white-space: normal; word-break: break-word;\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-right mr-2\"></i>\"Units\" (Member count) Mismatch\n            </button>\n        </h5>\n    </div>\n    <div id=\"collapseUP2\" class=\"collapse\">\n        <div class=\"card-body\">\n            <p>The amount of ration depends on the number of members (units) in the card. If units are missing, you get less ration.</p>\n            <p><strong>How to fix:</strong></p>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Apply for \"Addition of Member\" via a Jan Seva Kendra.</li>\n                <li>Submit the Aadhaar of the missing member.</li>\n                <li>Once verified, the unit count will increase in the portal and the FPS machine.</li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>"
}
